AU.name: Moshi Monsters™ Moshlings™ Theme Park
AU.description: Your monsterific adventure awaits! The Moshlings have lost their way around Amusement Isle and they need your help to round up their monster-mates and light up the magical Moshlings Theme Park. • Find the Lost Moshlings: With 60 Moshlings to find, players get to embark on exciting Moshi Missions to locate and reunite our Moshi friends. Play mini-games to unlock hints and tips to help you in your search. • Fun for all ages!: Suitable for a wide range of gamers, with easy-to-learn games and Moshi nuture modes for the youngest gamer, as well as exploration puzzles and arcade challenges for the more advanced. • Special Nintendo 3DS Features: Nintendo 3DS gamers will pass-and-play against their friends in StreetPass™ mode and compete for the golden trophy in highscore challenges and theme park mini-games.

BE.name: Moshi Monsters™ Moshlings™ Theme Park
BE.description: Une aventure monstruofantastique vous attend! Les Moshlings ont perdu leur chemin dans l’île de l’Amusement. Ils ont besoin de votre aide pour retrouver leurs monstres camarades et illuminer le magique parc à thème Moshlings.
